Source code availability
------------------------

The complete corresponding source code for this binary is at:

    https://github.com/<org>/bilbycast-edge/tree/v{VER}

(Replace `<org>/<VER>` at release-package time with the actual
GitHub organisation and tag.)

This variant does NOT include libx264 or libx265. For a
transcoding-capable binary see the -full variant, which bundles
libx264 + libx265 + NVENC and ships with its own NOTICE.full.

